name: Baby Boom
description: Temporal agents are kidnapping historically important newborns throughout time and space. Stop these agents while ensuring the babies are handled with care!
rules:
-- Unique Supply Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using any version of Tucker, B. Crusher, Worf, or G. La Forge will provide a bonus to Supply Missions.
-- Every Supply Mission you complete earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock Threshold Rewards!
-- Community Rewards are only available during Phase 1. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock these rewards before the phase change!
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Tucker, B. Crusher, Worf, or G. La Forge
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Supply Missions!

screens.text: "I think the worst thing about this crisis isn't the unpredictable anomalies, but the totally predictable bad actors taking advantage of it. Now we've got temporal agents preying on the most vulnerable: newborns."

"These agents seek to permanently alter the history of certain species by kidnapping infants who will grow up to become historically important figures. You are not to worry, I will use caution. I completed a holodeck training course on infant care."

"While Doctor Crusher and Worf's task force works on getting the babies safely away from the temporal agents, I'll be working on a way to stop them. Our arms are full, Captain, and we could sure use some help."
